{"word":"G1235 - διαγρηγορέω - diagrēgoréō - dee-ag-ray-gor-eh'-o - Be awake","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαγρηγορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diagrēgoréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ag-ray-gor-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be awake</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எழு"},{"paragraph":"to watch through, to remain awake to be fully awake"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G1127 - γρηγορεύω - grēgoreúō - gray-gor-yoo'-o/1127\">G1127</a>; to <i>waken thoroughly:</i> - be awake.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}